  ‘The Greatest Show’ is an adaptation of the 2017 film ‘The Greatest Showman’
  starring Hugh Jackman, Zac Efron, Michelle Williams, Rebecca Ferguson, and
  Zendaya. The musical tells the inspiring story of P.T. Barnum’s rise from a
  life of poverty to creating the Barnum & Bailey Circus, which became known as
  “The Greatest Show on Earth.” Despite the challenges and controversies along
  the way, Barnum remains determined to make his dreams come true and to offer a
  spectacle that unites people from all backgrounds.
