For 'The Greatest Show', I took on the role of Lead Lighting Designer and Operator.

A major focus of this production was conceptualizing a visual aesthetic that matched the massive, high-energy scale of the performance; I programmed the core lighting architecture to elevate the emotional beats of the story.

Beyond the creative design phase, I executed the show live from the console, ensuring that every cue synchronized perfectly with the performers on stage.
